spec_data.Name: php-symfony3-dotenv
spec_data.Description:
The Dotenv Component parses .env files to make environment variables stored in
them accessible via getenv(), $_ENV or $_SERVER.

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/Symfony3/Component/Dotenv/autoload.php

spec_data.Summary: Registers environment variables from a .env file (version 3)
